headline: Northern Trust Names New Head of Agricultural Properties
summary: PASADENA, Calif., December 16, 2024--Northern Trust announced today that John Onderdonk has been appointed National Practice Leader of Agricultural Properties. In this role, Onderdonk will oversee a multi-disciplinary group that manages and consults on agricultural properties such as farmland, ranches and timberland for Northern Trust’s clients.

headline: Northern Trust and NUS Forge Partnership to Advance Green Finance Innovation
summary: SINGAPORE, December 16, 2024--The partnership includes a tokenization initiative for green bonds, leveraging Northern Trust’s Matrix Zenith digital asset platform.
